     FGGAPP21 IT  F      36           EDISK
     E                    CD         50  1               EBCDIC
     E    GGAPP21         TABC   18 512  1   TABD    1   ASCII
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           EB     50
     C                     MOVEAEB        CD
     C                     Z-ADD1         J       20
     C           1         DO   50        J
     C                     MOVE CD,J      KEY     1
